{"tid":1000834,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"講咗咁耐 咁到底FTTB(光纖到大廈)同FTTH(光纖入屋)有幾大分別?","createTime":"2019-01-29T16:37:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T15:48:24.000Z","uid":84838,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"17e1e49ff977940219c5ac8c7e362620ecc67ae3","tid":1000834,"uid":84838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:37:46.000Z","msg":"GOOGLE完 睇晒全部討論之後發現好似又好似唔係真係好大分別咁<br />\n個速度真係會有分別咩?有人話FTTB拉既cat5e會被電波影響 會唔穩定 <br />\n但又唔見真係有人去屌FTTB好唔穩定 而且cat6同cat5c一樣做到1000mb<br />\n自己個朋友用緊FTTB 叫佢直插落牆用DFCA測速比我睇睇 <br />\n時延3毫秒 抖動0.8毫秒 下載792 上載917 睇落好似又冇咩事咁喎<br />\n自己就黎要換光纖 大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82069b3c6d994a97bd1ef7547c755f9fdb035a73","tid":1000834,"uid":227089,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:36:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"631649fb83f7fa55a58f504feb9ffdd8158a7bc9","tid":1000834,"uid":84838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82069b3c6d994a97bd1ef7547c755f9fdb035a73","tid":1000834,"uid":227089,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"17e1e49ff977940219c5ac8c7e362620ecc67ae3","tid":1000834,"uid":84838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:37:46.000Z","msg":"GOOGLE完 睇晒全部討論之後發現好似又好似唔係真係好大分別咁<br />\n個速度真係會有分別咩?有人話FTTB拉既cat5e會被電波影響 會唔穩定 <br />\n但又唔見真係有人去屌FTTB好唔穩定 而且cat6同cat5c一樣做到1000mb<br />\n自己個朋友用緊FTTB 叫佢直插落牆用DFCA測速比我睇睇 <br />\n時延3毫秒 抖動0.8毫秒 下載792 上載917 睇落好似又冇咩事咁喎<br />\n自己就黎要換光纖 大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:36:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T08:21:43.000Z","msg":"頭痛腳痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係我覺得冇分別 係冇真實數據支持<br />\n又話打風落雨會影響 樓上樓下BT會出事<br />\n但都係得一兩條友係到講"},{"pid":"b00895cfd047da366990a3269b8664ef92469bd8","tid":1000834,"uid":114720,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T08:24:57.000Z","msg":"其實冇乜大分別...<br />\n個人認為 fiber 俾你整斷左仲麻煩..一定要call ISP 搞<br />\n相反用LAN 線自己搞得掂"},{"pid":"07c6a12b78fbbc80285162570f64745d8c28938f","tid":1000834,"uid":12166,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T08:27:56.000Z","msg":"我認為LAN 線入屋最好<br />\n唔洗比電個轉換器"},{"pid":"e279057131b6c467c4fe68fec2c06322c37b144d","tid":1000834,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"07c6a12b78fbbc80285162570f64745d8c28938f","tid":1000834,"uid":12166,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T08:27:56.000Z","msg":"我認為LAN 線入屋最好<br />\n唔洗比電個轉換器"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T08:51:34.000Z","msg":"我而家日日夜夜養住部華為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60dc7cd399c7e6db009e78a29722eda79be9be4a","tid":1000834,"uid":39013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:21:33.000Z","msg":"cat5e...?<br />\n冇cat6都唔敢用"},{"pid":"2f87cf31adaba250dd6a192febbc89087a0cba21","tid":1000834,"uid":28057,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:31:34.000Z","msg":"理論上最快最直接係以前hkbn cat5 線入屋果種，<br />\n但係呢種方法成本最高<br />\n所以宜加pccw 同埋hkbn 都用晒FTTH , 成本低， 對一般客黎講冇乜分別"},{"pid":"feb8d425d1833bebdbc8d80a2f986dcf02bf2745","tid":1000834,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:33:14.000Z","msg":"普通用根本無咩分別<br />\n我用100M LAN線入戶，唔使插住隻光纖Modem<br />\n上網咪又係差唔多咁"},{"pid":"34f2f3a07ef42d6b3ef77f59389af27e085c5f49","tid":1000834,"uid":227089,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTi